    "permit_type": "Land Use ReviewType 2 procedureAD: Adjustment",
    "work_description": "Approval of the following four Adjustments for a new single-car garage: ¿Waive required 10-foot front setback (Zoning Code Section 33.110.220.B and Table 110-4);¿Waive required 5-foot side setback (33.110.220.B and Table 110-4);¿Waive required 18-foot garage entrance setback (33.110.220.B and Table 110-4); and ¿Allow a garage wall that faces a street to be closer to the street lot line than the longest street-facing wall of the dwelling unit (33.110.250.D.3). Approval is per the approved plans, Exhibits C.1 through C.2, signed and dated August 6, 2025, subject to the following conditions: A.A finalized building permit must be obtained to document the approved project. As part of the permit application submittal, each of the site plans and any additional drawings must reflect the information and design approved by this land use review as indicated in Exhibits C.1-C.2. The sheets on which this information appears must be labeled, \"Proposal and design as approved in Case File # LU 25-050099 AD.¿",
